<!-- MtToolbar.vue -->
<template>
  <v-toolbar :dense="dense" elevation="3">
    <v-toolbar-title>{{ title }}</v-toolbar-title>
    <MtIconButton
      icon-name="mdi-home"
      height="16"
      :width="30"
      class="ml-1"
      @click="backHome"
    ></MtIconButton>
  </v-toolbar>
</template>

<script>
import MtIconButton from "@/components/MtIconButton.vue";

export default {
  components: {
    MtIconButton,
  },
  props: {
    color: { type: String, required: false, default: undefined },
    elevation: { type: [Number, String], required: false, default: undefined },
    dense: { type: Boolean, required: false, default: true },
    title: { type: String, required: false, default: undefined },
  },
  methods: {
    backHome: function () {
      this.$router.push("/");
    },
  },
};
</script>
